{"id":158241,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/澳广-香港15万人烛光纪念六四22周年/","date":"2011-06-06T00:30:18Z","modified":"2011-06-06T00:30:18Z","title":"澳广 | 香港15万人烛光纪念六四22周年","content":"<div>\n<p>香港15万人烛光纪念六四22周年</p>\n<p>香港支联会在维园举行六四22周年烛光晚会，大会组织者说，参加者坐满维园6个足球场和草地，估计有超过15万人参加。警方表示，高峰期时，维园有7万7千人。.</p>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td>\n<div>\n<p>2011 年 06 月 05 日</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/articles/s3235915.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/decrease.gif\" alt=\"Decrease\" title=\"Decrease\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/articles/s3235915.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/standard.gif\" alt=\"Standard\" title=\"Standard\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/articles/s3235915.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/increase.gif\" alt=\"Increase\" title=\"Increase\" /></a> | <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.abc.net.au/cgi-bin/common/mailto/mailto-nojs_query.pl?http://www.abc.net.au/ra/chinese/articles/s3235915.htm&#038;presname=/ra\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/email.gif\" alt=\"Email\" title=\"Email\" /></a> | <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.abc.net.au/cgi-bin/common/printfriendly.pl?http://www.abc.net.au/ra/chinese/articles/s3235915.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/print.gif\" alt=\"Print\" title=\"Print\" /></a> | <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/articles/s3235915.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/favourite.gif\" alt=\"Favourite\" title=\"Favourite\" /></a></p>\n<p>香港支联会在维园举行六四22周年烛光晚会，大会组织者说，参加者坐满维园6个足球场和草地，估计有超过15万人参加。警方表示，高峰期时，维园有7万7千人。</p>\n<p>支联会主席李卓人说，已故主席司徒华会看到，今年有不少年轻面孔参加，认为已能做到薪火相传，相信司徒华会感到安慰。</p>\n<p>烛光晚会在晚上8时许开始，播出司徒华生前拍